Package com.intellij.openapi.externalSystem.service.remote.wrapper

Class ExternalSystemFacadeWrapper<S extends ExternalSystemExecutionSettings>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.externalSystem.service.remote.wrapper.ExternalSystemFacadeWrapper<S>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalSystemTaskAware, RemoteExternalSystemFacade<S>, java.rmi.Remote

    public class ExternalSystemFacadeWrapper<S extends ExternalSystemExecutionSettings>
extends java.lang.Object
implements RemoteExternalSystemFacade<S>
    This class acts as a point where target remote external system services are proxied.

    Check service wrapper contracts for more details.

    Thread-safe.
